### =========================================
### 1️⃣ Register User
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "ashish",
  "email": "ashish@gmail.com",
  "password": "ashish123"
}

###

### =========================================
### 2️⃣ Login User
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "ashish@gmail.com",
  "password": "ashish123"
}

###

### =========================================
### 3️⃣ Chat - Send Message (USE TOKEN FROM LOGIN)
### Replace TOKEN with actual token from login response
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "userId": "6998c7320ff0708150423515",
  "message": "Should I give discount to loyal customers?",
  "category": "pricing"
}

###

### =========================================
### 4️⃣ Get Chat History (USE TOKEN FROM LOGIN)
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/chat/history
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### =========================================
### 5️⃣ Get Conversation Details (USE TOKEN FROM LOGIN)
### Replace CONVERSATION_ID with actual ID
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/chat/CONVERSATION_ID
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

###

### =========================================
### 6️⃣ Test RAG Context (TEST ENDPOINT)
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/rag-context?userId=YOUR_USER_ID&message=pricing

###

### =========================================
### 7️⃣ Validate API Key (TEST ENDPOINT)
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/validate-api

###

### =========================================
### 8️⃣ Get Stats (TEST ENDPOINT)
### =========================================
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/stats?userId=YOUR_USER_ID

###

### =========================================
### 9️⃣ Generate Response (TEST ENDPOINT)
### =========================================
POST http://localhost:5000/api/test/generate-response
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userMessage": "Should I give discount?",
  "userId": "YOUR_USER_ID"
}